            "origClipLength": 77,
            "voiceIdx": -1,
            "pathId": -2943947912959331896,
            "blockIdx": 3
        },
        {
            "jpName": "モノローグ",
            "enName": "",
            "jpText": "――……別世界は、確かに在る。\n自分はそれを、知っている。",
            "enText": "…The other world exists. \nI know that for certain.",
            "nextBlock": 5,
            "origClipLength": 82,
            "voiceIdx": -1,
            "pathId": -4816297733466156027,
            "blockIdx": 4
        },
        {
            "jpName": "モノローグ",
            "enName": "",
            "jpText": "ステイゴールドがいない、『日本ダービー』。\nステイゴールドが\n走れなかった『日本ダービー』。",
            "enText": "A Japan Derby without Stay Gold. \nA Japan Derby Stay Gold could \nnot participate.",
            "nextBlock": 6,
            "origClipLength": 105,
            "voiceIdx": -1,
            "pathId": 888239344263482483,
            "blockIdx": 5
        },
        {
            "jpName": "モノローグ",
            "enName": "",
            "jpText": "それは、確かに在った。\nそして、別世界にとってはそれが――\n史実となっているのだろう。",
            "enText": "That was the reality in the other world. \nIn fact, this affair cemented itself as — \n<i>a historical fact. </i>",
            "nextBlock": 7,
            "origClipLength": 101,
            "voiceIdx": -1,
            "pathId": 3474051478451405474,
            "blockIdx": 6
        },
        {
            "jpName": "モノローグ",
            "enName": "",
            "jpText": "けれど……この世界は――――！！！",
            "enText": "However… In this world of ours —!!!",
            "nextBlock": 8,
            "origClipLength": 67,
            "voiceIdx": -1,
            "pathId": 648583781552603751,
            "blockIdx": 7
        },
        {
            "jpName": "ステイゴールド",
            "enName": "Stay Gold",
